This is the software that runs the BEACON station. 
It depends on libnuphase for talking to the boards. 

It consists of several programs: 

nuphase-acq:   Data Acquisition (nuphase-acq.c)
nuphase-copy:  Data copying to RadProc    (nuphase-copy.c)
nuphase-hk:   Housekeeping  / power control daemon     (nuphase-hk.c)
nuphase-startup: Startup process that does basically nothing in beacon. (nuphase-startup.c) 



Influential environmental variables: 

  NUPHASE_CONFIG_DIR : defines the directory to read config files from 
  


